At the height of the intifada .. Adoption of a million dollars & quot;
01 Nov 2019, 06:45 by Lebanon 24
Observers asked how the government approved at the 21st session $ 1 million for an education program for a ministry in the midst of the intifada, which was published in the official gazette yesterday, a benefit for one of the ministers, according to the secrets of the "Republic."
